{"tid":1539021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"慘啦 condom仔差唔多要比人背叛 自己諗啦","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:23:06.000Z","uid":208492,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2710cffd0ae180687cf1cf3adbbf08233168fa35","tid":1539021,"uid":208492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:35:55.000Z","msg":"今次就撒回<br />\n下次就獨委會<br />\n如果我地繼續出黎<br />\n下次政府就用埋condom仔黎平息<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ncondom仔正式變真。condom仔<br />\ncondom仔自己諗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早提左你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181f61ff3808b55bb673df0e2c623402e6d12b4a","tid":1539021,"uid":4075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:36:04.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求   缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">FIVE DEMANDS - NOT ONE LESS</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>9月7 機場<br />\n9月8 美領</strong></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"98563451df1d2363b9a855fbea35a27ab71a7d65","tid":1539021,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"不要說推<br />\n試著說<br />\n【831 太子站目擊者立法會見記者】<br />\n-有一個人失蹤<br />\n-有機會有一個人死左 比警察打左半個鐘 嘔白泡 差佬見佢冇反應 之後冇打 二三十分鐘後由消防員 非救護人員 送走 完全冇反應<br />\n-差佬同佢地講想屌佢地係正常<br />\n-有被捕人士係警署被非禮 (摸胸)<br />\n-係警署去廁所時不能關門 而當時有其他性別既警員在場<br />\n-有日本人被捕 警方拒絕比佢聯繫大使館<br />\n-目擊者話傷者係送去瑪嘉烈唔係廣華<br />\n-速龍落電梯 踩住市民背部甚至頭部落"},{"pid":"1163c80fa4988ac64e44a57faf3ae74e92583dd7","tid":1539021,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98563451df1d2363b9a855fbea35a27ab71a7d65","tid":1539021,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"不要說推<br />\n試著說<br />\n【831 太子站目擊者立法會見記者】<br />\n-有一個人失蹤<br />\n-有機會有一個人死左 比警察打左半個鐘 嘔白泡 差佬見佢冇反應 之後冇打 二三十分鐘後由消防員 非救護人員 送走 完全冇反應<br />\n-差佬同佢地講想屌佢地係正常<br />\n-有被捕人士係警署被非禮 (摸胸)<br />\n-係警署去廁所時不能關門 而當時有其他性別既警員在場<br />\n-有日本人被捕 警方拒絕比佢聯繫大使館<br />\n-目擊者話傷者係送去瑪嘉烈唔係廣華<br />\n-速龍落電梯 踩住市民背部甚至頭部落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">8/9 美領事館 塞爆港島</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪、減少淘寶<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少掂中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.04"},{"pid":"d97161e87685e84fc70c6fa4acbdadbda457c9cd","tid":1539021,"uid":208492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:40:50.000Z","msg":"condom仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8e8d1a5feb0